{"body": "It can be a problem if you want to implement a helper method with link_to_unless.\r\n\r\n```ruby\r\ndef do_something(condtion)\r\n  \"Do something with #{link_to_unless(condition, '<b>x</b>', 'github.com')}\".html_safe\r\nend\r\ndo_something(false)\r\n# => \"Do something with <a href=\\\"github.com\\\">&lt;b&gt;x&lt;/b&gt;</a>\"\r\ndo_something(true)\r\n# => \"Do something with <b>x</b>\" # x is bolded this time\r\n```\r\n\r\nI think it is very confusing.", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/19266736", "created_at": "2013-06-11T14:52:50Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/10910#issuecomment-19266736", "updated_at": "2013-06-11T14:52:50Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 10910, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dtaniwaki/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dtaniwaki/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dtaniwaki/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/dtaniwaki", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dtaniwaki/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/dtaniwaki", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dtaniwaki/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/892593b2b246582a26015e3bbf4bb1c7?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F9507d78f9c9184a70f4a559ef929d915.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dtaniwaki/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dtaniwaki/received_events", "gravatar_id": "892593b2b246582a26015e3bbf4bb1c7", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dtaniwaki/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "dtaniwaki", "type": "User", "id": 1162120, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dtaniwaki/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "5237daacbd3543c151008739"}, "id": 19266736, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/10910"}
